==English==

===Verb===
'''powerbock'''

# Activity involving running, jumping and performing various acrobatics with the aid of vertically mounted curved springs attached to one's legs for exercise, pleasure or entertainment purposes. Based on the name of the German inventor of this type of device, Alexander Böck. Also referred to as bocking. See photo [[http://www.powerskip.de/P01.jpg]]
#: ''The boy's favorite place to '''powerbock''' is in the park.''